event_title.description_long:
MadPiano Collection Concept Store will open the gates in a new location downtown: Stelea Spataru 13, ground floor, room 2 in what has previously been a Police Station, Manasia Hub is a multicultural hub and a bar with a quiet garden where you will find real people & real stories.
For those passionate about music, vinyl, dj-ing, urban-art and clubbing...we are back!
The costom made funiture and design of the shop wouldn't be possible without the contribution of Mihai Morarescu and Irina Maria Morarescu who were with us since the beginning of MadPiano since 2014. Special thanks to them!
We started at the so called gallery at Aviatorilor 9 along with the project Visionatura, then make a big move to establish our Records Store to Cazzavillans 12 in 2016. And now another 2 years later ending up here at Manasia Hub after a long journey.
From 6PM till midnight or more, at turntables, will be spinning some vinyl for us: Boddo and Antonio Bajanaru (GUSH)
